No. —. Original.

Ex parte: In the Matter of Howard B. Manington et al., Petitioners. Motion for leave to file petition submitted April 3, 1911. Decided April 10, 1911. Mr. B. W. McCoy and Mr. Smith W. Bennett for the petitioner. No one opposing. Per Curiam.

Motion for leave to file petition for writ of mandamus denied. See Ex parte Harding, 219 U. S. 363, decided at this term.
